				Where an alternative solution is needed to protect a pipeline from pressure surges, our compressor controlled surge tank systems can provide optimum transient pressure protection against unplanned events like an unexpected pump shut-down, or valve openings, or closures on a water distribution main, or firewater system.<!--Where an alternative solution is needed to protect a pipeline from pressure surges, our compressor controlled surge tank systems can provide optimum transient pressure protection against unplanned events like an unexpected pump shut-down, or valve openings, or closures on a water distribution main, or firewater system.--><br />

