            <h3 class="media-heading"><strong>

				Gas Pulsation Dampeners and Compressor Pulsation Analysis (API618)<!--Gas Pulsation Dampeners and Compressor Pulsation Analysis (API618)--></strong></h3>

				The simple action of a positive displacement gas compressor, whether a single or multi-stage machine, will often cause resonances in the attached pipework which in turn can lead to mechanical failure of the piping, and/or the structure to which it is attached. Our Gas Pulsation Dampener's are tuned to eliminate compressor pulsation and thereby eliminate the driving forces that can break your pipework. Our solutions are proven through analysis to API618 and on-site measurement of the pressure pulsations.<!-- The simple action of a positive displacement gas compressor, whether a single or multi-stage machine, will often cause reasonances in the attached pipework which in turn can lead to mechanical failure of the piping, and/or the structure to which it is attached. Computational analysis to API618 will provide the necessary reOur Gas Pulsation Dampener's are tuned to eliminate compressor pulsation and thereby eliminate the driving forces that can break your pipework. &nbsp;Our solutions are proven through analysis to API618 and on-site measurement of the pressure pulsations. --><br /><strong><a href="/pages/14_API674_Pressure_Pulsation_Analysis.php">Find out more</a></strong>

